title: LIBERTARIANISM  An Ideological History (1)
itunes:author: Toby Buckle
itunes:summary: By audience selection, I cover the intellectual and ideological history of libertarianism.   What were its origins and what was is reacting against? I also attempt to place these developments in their historical context and discuss how they affected the world, our current institutions, and even how we think now.
